---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Onchain AMM — Permissionless Markets">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Permissionless Markets</span><span class="lang-zh">無需許可的市場</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">Onchain AMM</span><span class="lang-zh">鏈上自動化做市商</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      <span class="lang-en">Permissionless financial markets where anyone can list, trade, or provide liquidity — no exchange approval, no designated market maker, no trading hours.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">無需許可嘅金融市場 — 任何人都可以上市、交易或提供流動性，唔使交易所審批、唔使指定做市商、唔使交易時段。</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Stats grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-12">
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$1-2B</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Uniswap daily vol</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap日交易量</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">24/7</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Markets open</span><span class="lang-zh">市場全天候</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">x·y=k</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">Pricing formula</span><span class="lang-zh">定價公式</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1000s</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-1">
          <span class="lang-en">New tokens daily</span><span class="lang-zh">每日新代幣</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">In traditional markets, listing a new security requires exchange approval, regulatory filing, and a designated market maker agreement. Onchain, you create a liquidity pool and the market exists. No application, no approval, no trading hours. Uniswap, the largest decentralized exchange on Ethereum, processes $1 to $2 billion in daily volume. Raydium and Meteora handle comparable volume on Solana. Thousands of new tokens are listed every day — permissionless financial markets, operating 24/7.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">在傳統市場，上市一隻新證券需要交易所審批、監管備案同指定做市商協議。在鏈上，你建立一個liquidity pool，市場就存在。無需申請，無需審批，無交易時段。Uniswap，Ethereum上最大嘅去中心化交易所，日交易量$10至$20億。Raydium同Meteora在Solana上處理相當嘅交易量。每日有數千隻新代幣上市 — 無需許可嘅金融市場，24/7運作。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">How It Works: The Constant Product Formula</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">運作原理：恆定乘積公式</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">An automated market maker replaces the traditional orderbook with a mathematical formula. A pool contains two tokens — say ETH and USDC — and their quantities maintain a constant product: <span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono">x × y = k</span>. When you buy Token A, the pool's supply of Token A decreases while Token B increases, and Token A's price rises automatically. No orderbook, no market maker placing orders — a smart contract quotes prices based on supply and demand.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">AMM用數學公式取代傳統orderbook。一個池入面有兩隻代幣 — 例如ETH同USDC — 佢哋嘅數量維持恆定乘積：<span class="text-cyan-400 font-mono">x × y = k</span>。你買Token A，池入面Token A供應就減少、Token B增加，Token A嘅price自動升。唔使orderbook，唔使做市商掛單 — smart contract根據供需自動報價。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Aggregators like Jupiter (Solana) and 1inch (Ethereum) automatically route trades across dozens of pools to find the best price. Settlement is instant — seconds, not T+1 or T+2. Assets stay in your wallet throughout. Non-custodial, no exchange intermediary.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">聚合器好似Jupiter（Solana）同1inch（Ethereum）會自動幫你搵幾十個池入面最好嘅price。結算即時 — 秒級，唔係T+1或T+2。資產全程留喺你錢包。Non-custodial，唔經交易所。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Three Things You Can Do</span><span class="lang-zh">三件你可以做嘅嘢</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">1. Trade — onchain swap.</span> Any token pair can be swapped as long as someone has created a pool. No listing requirement. This is the basic use case: buy and sell tokens with instant settlement and self-custody.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">1. 交易 — 鏈上swap。</span>只要有人建立咗池，任何代幣對都可以swap。唔使上市審批。呢個係最基本嘅用法：即時結算、自己hold住個錢包嚟買賣代幣。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">2. Provide liquidity — be the market maker.</span> Deposit two tokens into a pool and earn trading fees from every swap. In finance terms, this is going long two assets and short volatility. The P&L of the short vol position is called impermanent loss: when one token's price moves significantly relative to the other, your position is worth less than simply holding both tokens. Stablecoin pairs (USDC/USDT) offer low fees of 0.01 to 0.05% per swap with minimal impermanent loss — comparable to money market yields. New token launches can carry fee rates of 50 to 99%, generating significant short-term returns, but the underlying tokens are extremely volatile and frequently go to zero.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">2. 提供流動性 — 做做市商。</span>將兩隻代幣存入池中，從每筆交易賺取費用。用金融語言講，呢個係做多兩種資產加做空波動率。做空波動率倉位嘅盈虧叫做無常損失：當一隻代幣嘅價格相對另一隻大幅變動，你嘅倉位價值低過單純持有兩隻代幣。穩定幣對（USDC/USDT）每筆交易提供0.01至0.05%嘅低費率，無常損失最小 — 與貨幣市場收益相當。新代幣發行可有50至99%嘅費率，產生可觀嘅短期回報，但底層代幣波動極大且經常歸零。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">3. Launch a token — permissionless IPO.</span> Platforms like PumpFun and Raydium LaunchLab allow anyone to launch a token in seconds. Bonding curve pricing means early buyers get lower prices, and more buyers push the price up. At a certain market cap, the token automatically migrates to an AMM pool and becomes a fully tradeable market. Essentially a permissionless IPO — no underwriter, no prospectus, no lock-up period. Thousands launch daily. 99% are junk, but the infrastructure itself is a fundamental financial primitive: permissionless capital formation.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">3. 發行代幣 — 無需許可嘅IPO。</span>PumpFun同Raydium LaunchLab等平台俾任何人幾秒之內launch一隻代幣。Bonding curve定價：早期買家price低，越多人買price越高。到一定market cap，代幣自動migrate去AMM池變成fully tradeable嘅market。本質上就係permissionless IPO — 冇underwriter、冇招股書、冇鎖定期。每日launch幾千隻。99%係垃圾，但呢個基礎設施本身係一個基本金融原語：唔使批准嘅資本形成。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- Uniswap Versions -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Uniswap: The Evolution of AMM Design</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap：AMM設計嘅演進</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Uniswap invented the modern AMM and has iterated through four major versions, each solving a specific problem. Understanding the progression explains why Solana AMMs look the way they do — they're all building on ideas Uniswap pioneered.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Uniswap發明咗現代AMM，經歷咗四個主要版本，每個版本解決一個特定問題。理解呢個演進就會明白點解Solana嘅AMM係咁設計 — 全部都係建基於Uniswap開創嘅概念。</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Uniswap v2 — The Original x·y=k</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap v2 — 最初嘅 x·y=k</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The model described above. You deposit equal value of two tokens, and the formula handles pricing. Simple, elegant, but inefficient: your liquidity is spread across the entire price range from 0 to infinity. If ETH trades at $3,000, most of your capital sits in ranges (like $0–$100 or $50,000+) where no trades ever happen. <span class="text-white">Result: ~0.5% of deposited capital is actively used at any time.</span></span>
        <span class="lang-zh">即係上面講嘅模型。你存入等值嘅兩隻token，公式負責定價。簡單、優雅，但效率低：你嘅流動性分散喺由0到無限嘅整個價格範圍。如果ETH交易價$3,000，你大部分資金坐喺啲永遠唔會有交易嘅範圍（好似$0–$100或$50,000+）。<span class="text-white">結果：任何時候只有~0.5%嘅存入資本被用到。</span></span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Uniswap v3 — Concentrated Liquidity</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap v3 — 集中流動性</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The big breakthrough (2021). Instead of spreading liquidity across all prices, LPs choose a <span class="text-white font-medium">specific price range</span> to deploy their capital. If you think ETH will trade between $2,800 and $3,200, you only provide liquidity in that range — same capital, but up to <span class="text-white">4,000x more capital efficient</span> than v2.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">2021年嘅重大突破。唔再將流動性分散喺所有價格，LP揀一個<span class="text-white font-medium">特定價格範圍</span>嚟deploy資金。如果你覺得ETH會喺$2,800到$3,200之間交易，你只喺呢個範圍提供流動性 — 同樣嘅資金，但資本效率最高<span class="text-white">提升4,000倍</span>。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The tradeoff: active management. If price moves out of your range, your position stops earning fees and becomes 100% one token (impermanent loss maximized). Professional LPs constantly adjust their ranges — this is essentially running a market-making strategy, not passive income.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">代價係：要主動管理。如果價格離開你嘅範圍，你嘅position停止賺fee，變成100%單一token（無常損失最大化）。專業LP要不停調整範圍 — 本質上係跑一個做市策略，唔係被動收入。</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Uniswap v4 — Hooks & Custom Logic</span><span class="lang-zh">Uniswap v4 — Hooks同自定義邏輯</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Released 2024. Uniswap v4 introduces <span class="text-white font-medium">"hooks"</span> — custom code that runs before or after swaps, liquidity changes, or pool creation. This turns Uniswap from a fixed protocol into a <span class="text-white">programmable liquidity platform</span>. Examples of what hooks enable:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">2024年推出。Uniswap v4引入<span class="text-white font-medium">「hooks」</span>— 喺swap、流動性變更或pool creation之前或之後運行嘅自定義代碼。將Uniswap由一個固定protocol變成<span class="text-white">可編程嘅流動性平台</span>。Hooks可以做到嘅例子：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Dynamic fees</span> — adjust fee rate based on volatility (higher fees during volatile periods)</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">動態費率</span> — 根據波動性調整費率（波動大時收更高費用）</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">TWAMM</span> — time-weighted average market maker for large orders that execute gradually over time</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">TWAMM</span> — 時間加權平均做市商，大單隨時間逐步執行</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Limit orders</span> — onchain limit orders that execute when price hits your target</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">限價單</span> — 價格到你嘅目標就自動執行嘅鏈上限價單</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">KYC/compliance</span> — restrict pool access to verified addresses</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">KYC/合規</span> — 限制pool只畀已驗證地址使用</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">v4 also uses a "singleton" architecture — all pools live in one contract, dramatically reducing gas costs for multi-hop swaps. For finance professionals: v4 is essentially Uniswap becoming an <span class="text-white">exchange platform</span> rather than an exchange, similar to what Hyperliquid did with HIP-3.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">v4仲用「singleton」架構 — 所有pools住喺同一個contract入面，大幅降低multi-hop swap嘅gas成本。對金融從業者嚟講：v4本質上係Uniswap由一間交易所變成一個<span class="text-white">交易所平台</span>，類似Hyperliquid用HIP-3做嘅嘢。</span>
      </p>

      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <!-- Solana AMM Landscape -->
      <!-- ============================================ -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Solana: A Different AMM Ecosystem</span><span class="lang-zh">Solana：唔同嘅AMM生態</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Solana's low fees and fast blocks (400ms) enable AMM designs that aren't practical on Ethereum. The result is a richer variety of AMM types, each optimized for different use cases. Here are the major ones:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Solana嘅低費用同快速出塊（400ms）令到喺Ethereum上唔實際嘅AMM設計變得可行。結果係更豐富嘅AMM類型，每種針對唔同用途優化。以下係主要嘅幾種：</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">PumpFun — Bonding Curve AMM (Token Launches)</span><span class="lang-zh">PumpFun — 聯合曲線AMM（Token Launch專用）</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">PumpFun isn't a general-purpose AMM — it's a <span class="text-white font-medium">token launch platform</span> with a built-in bonding curve. Anyone pays ~$2 to create a token. The bonding curve acts as the initial AMM: early buyers get low prices, each subsequent buy pushes the price up along a fixed curve. When the bonding curve fills (hits ~$69K market cap), the token automatically "graduates" and migrates to PumpSwap (PumpFun's own AMM) or previously to Raydium.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">PumpFun唔係通用AMM — 係一個<span class="text-white font-medium">token launch平台</span>，內建bonding curve。任何人用~$2就可以開一隻幣。Bonding curve充當初始AMM：早期買家price低，每次買入沿固定曲線推高價格。當bonding curve填滿（到~$69K market cap），token自動「畢業」並migrate去PumpSwap（PumpFun自己嘅AMM）或者之前係去Raydium。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Key numbers:</span> Over 10 million tokens launched on PumpFun since 2024. ~1-2% survive past the first week. The platform generates significant fee revenue — the launch mechanism itself is the product. Creator fees (coin creator fee) were introduced in 2026, letting deployers earn from trading on their token.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">關鍵數字：</span>自2024年起PumpFun上launch咗超過1000萬隻token。大約1-2%撐過第一個禮拜。平台產生可觀嘅fee收入 — launch機制本身就係產品。2026年推出creator fees（幣creator費用），令deployer可以從佢哋嘅token交易中賺錢。</span>
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4">
        <a href={`${base}/products/amm/pumpfun`} class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-sm">PumpFun deep dive →</a>
        <a href={`${base}/products/amm/pumpswap`} class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-sm">PumpSwap deep dive →</a>
        <a href={`${base}/products/amm/raydium-launchlab`} class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-sm">LaunchLab deep dive →</a>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Meteora DAMM (Dynamic AMM) — Fee-Optimized Pools</span><span class="lang-zh">Meteora DAMM（Dynamic AMM）— 費率優化池</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Meteora's DAMM (now in v2) is a constant-product AMM like Uniswap v2, but with <span class="text-white font-medium">dynamic fee schedules</span> that make it uniquely suited for LP fee capture. Key features:</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Meteora嘅DAMM（而家係v2）係類似Uniswap v2嘅恆定乘積AMM，但加咗<span class="text-white font-medium">動態費率schedule</span>，令佢特別適合LP捕捉fee。主要特點：</span>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Time-decaying fees</span> — pool can start at 99% fee and decay linearly to 10% over 24 hours. Early traders pay massive fees; LPs who are first to provide liquidity earn the most.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">時間衰減費率</span> — pool可以由99%開始，24小時內線性衰減到10%。早期trader付巨額費用；最早提供流動性嘅LP賺最多。</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Collect-fee-mode</span> — fees can be collected only in SOL (Token B), making LP returns predictable in SOL terms regardless of the base token's price action.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">收費模式</span> — 可以設定只收SOL（Token B）fee，令LP回報喺SOL計價下可預測，唔受base token價格波動影響。</span></li>
        <li><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white">Permanent lock</span> — liquidity can be permanently locked, creating trust for traders that the pool won't be rug-pulled.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white">永久鎖定</span> — 流動性可以永久鎖定，令trader信任個pool唔會被rug pull。</span></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">DAMM v2 is where most of the LP fee-capture strategy in Solana DeFi operates. When a new memecoin launches and generates high trading volume, LPs race to create high-fee DAMM v2 pools to capture fees from aggregator-routed trades.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">DAMM v2係Solana DeFi入面大部分LP fee-capture策略嘅運作地。當一隻新memecoin launch並產生高交易量，LP爭住開高fee嘅DAMM v2 pool嚟捕捉aggregator路由嘅交易費用。</span>
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4">
        <a href={`${base}/products/amm/meteora-damm`} class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-sm">DAMM v2 deep dive →</a>
        <a href={`${base}/products/amm/meteora-dbc`} class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 text-sm">Meteora DBC deep dive →</a>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">CLMM — Concentrated Liquidity (Raydium, Orca)</span><span class="lang-zh">CLMM — 集中流動性（Raydium、Orca）</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Solana's version of Uniswap v3. <span class="text-white font-medium">Raydium CLMM</span> and <span class="text-white font-medium">Orca Whirlpools</span> both implement concentrated liquidity — LPs choose specific price ranges to deploy capital, dramatically improving capital efficiency.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Solana版本嘅Uniswap v3。<span class="text-white font-medium">Raydium CLMM</span>同<span class="text-white font-medium">Orca Whirlpools</span>都實現咗concentrated liquidity — LP揀特定價格範圍deploy資金，大幅提升資本效率。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The advantage over Ethereum CLMMs: Solana's 400ms block times and near-zero fees make range adjustments practical. On Ethereum, adjusting your LP range costs $5–50 in gas, making frequent rebalancing expensive. On Solana, it costs fractions of a cent. This means active LP management strategies that are prohibitively expensive on Ethereum are viable on Solana.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">相比Ethereum CLMMs嘅優勢：Solana嘅400ms出塊時間同接近零嘅費用令調整range變得實際。喺Ethereum，調整LP range要$5–50 gas費，頻繁rebalancing好貴。喺Solana，只需幾分錢嘅零頭。即係喺Ethereum上成本高到唔實際嘅active LP管理策略，喺Solana上行得通。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Orca also introduced <span class="text-white">adaptive fee pools</span> — the fee rate automatically adjusts based on market conditions, similar to what Uniswap v4 hooks can do but built natively into the protocol.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Orca仲推出咗<span class="text-white">自適應費率pool</span> — 費率根據市場條件自動調整，類似Uniswap v4 hooks可以做嘅嘢，但原生built into protocol。</span>
      </p>

