      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">Meteora DLMM — Discretized Liquidity (Bin-Based)</span><span class="lang-zh">Meteora DLMM — 離散化流動性（基於Bin）</span>
      </h3>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Meteora's DLMM (Discretized Liquidity Market Maker) takes a different approach to concentrated liquidity. Instead of continuous price ranges (like Uniswap v3 / Raydium CLMM), DLMM divides the price space into discrete <span class="text-white font-medium">"bins"</span>. Each bin holds liquidity at a specific price point, and LPs can distribute their capital across any combination of bins.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Meteora嘅DLMM（離散化流動性做市商）用唔同嘅方式做concentrated liquidity。唔同於連續價格範圍（好似Uniswap v3 / Raydium CLMM），DLMM將價格空間分成離散嘅<span class="text-white font-medium">「bins」</span>。每個bin喺特定價格點持有流動性，LP可以將資金分配到任何bin嘅組合。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Key difference from CLMM: in a CLMM, only one LP position is active at a time (the one whose range contains the current price). In DLMM, <span class="text-white">only the active bin trades</span> — this means zero slippage within a bin (fixed price until the bin's liquidity is consumed), then price jumps to the next bin. This creates a step-function price curve rather than a smooth curve.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">同CLMM嘅關鍵分別：喺CLMM入面，同一時間只有一個LP position活躍（包含當前價格嘅嗰個range）。喺DLMM，<span class="text-white">只有active bin交易</span> — 即係一個bin入面零滑點（固定價格直到bin嘅流動性用完），然後價格跳去下一個bin。呢個創建嘅係階梯式價格曲線而唔係smooth曲線。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">DLMM is particularly popular for volatile token pairs where LPs want precise control over their exposure at each price level. The bin-based system also makes it easier to implement strategies like one-sided liquidity (providing only sell-side at higher prices).</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">DLMM特別受歡迎嘅場景係波動大嘅token pair，LP想精確控制每個價格水平嘅exposure。Bin-based系統仲令實現策略變得更容易，好似單邊流動性（只喺更高價格提供賣盤）。</span>
      </p>

